tolong saya
ketika saya berada dalam bahaya?

7
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:11,630
Bai Jue pernah beritahu saya,

8
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,520
kuasa iblis amat menakutkan

9
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:15,080
kerana ia akan melekat pada luka

10
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:16,960
dan menghakis kuasa dewa
secara perlahan-lahan.

11
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:19,550
Ia mesti dihapuskan segera.

12
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:21,670
Kalau tidak, asas saya akan terpengaruh.

13
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:24,670
Namun,

14
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:26,880
saya tak pernah lihat

15
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,950
herba yang disebut oleh dia

16
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:30,880
di Alam Termulia yang luas ini.

17
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,920
Besarnya Lingzhi ini.

18
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:43,270
Nampaknya, ia lebih tua
daripada Lingzhi di Alam Dewa.

19
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,270
Kemungkinan besar ia boleh digunakan.

20
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,230
Pedang Gu Di,

21
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,110
tak sangka awak ada bakat ini.

22
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,040
Bakat awak dibazirkan
semasa kita berada di Alam Dewa.

23
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:02,000
Asalkan awak berada di sisi saya,

24
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,790
saya tak payah risau lagi.

25
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,720
(Ini lingzhi iblis.)

26
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,230
(Jika awak termakan,)

27
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,550
(bukan sahaja demam, bahkan koma.)

28
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,600
(Yang ini pun awak tak dapat bezakan.)

29
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,110
(Sia-sia sahaja usaha saya.)

30
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:31,940
♪Hujan membanjir jadi lautan♪

31
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,670
Entah apa

32
00:05:34,670 --> 00:05:36,720
yang mereka sedang buat sekarang.

33
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,230
Sudah pasti Yue Mi

34
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:40,350
menjemput dewa yang pandai bercerita.

35
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:43,110
Apakah cerita pada hari ini?

36
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,880
Entah-entah saya pernah mendengarnya.

37
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,510
Pedang Gu Di,

38
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:51,320
sudah pasti bunga anggerik awak
tak berkesan.

39
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,760
Setelah saya makan,

40
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,270
keadaan saya tak bertambah baik.

41
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:56,320
Malah, saya rasa pening kepala.

42
00:05:57,400 --> 00:06:00,720
♪Cinta saya bagai purnama
menerangi gunung dan lautan♪

43
00:06:02,550 --> 00:06:06,200
Sebagai Dewa Utama Tiga Alam,

44
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:09,550
saya pengsan atas sebab sebatang herba.

45
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:12,320
Sudah pasti mereka akan
mengetawakan saya.

46
00:06:14,270 --> 00:06:15,550
Shang Gu,

47
00:06:15,550 --> 00:06:17,200
jangan sesekali tertidur.

48
00:06:18,350 --> 00:06:20,600
Tempat ini amat bahaya.

49
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,200
Sudah pasti awak amat penat.

50
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,200
Tidurlah.

51
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:42,860
♪Lihat betapa banyak kali penghijrahan
burung sambil saksikan peredaran tahun♪

52
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:49,340
♪Nantikan awak tanpa rasa kesal,
tiada orang yang pernah mengganti awak♪

53
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:51,830
♪Semoga peristiwa masa lampau diatasi♪

54
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:53,000
Ketulan Ais,

55
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,830
saya berusaha untuk

56
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:56,760
menjadi gadis yang secocok dengan awak.

57
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:00,510
Awak mesti kekal sama

58
00:07:00,510 --> 00:07:02,200
selama seribu tahun ini,

59
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,160
bersikap dingin

60
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:05,920
terhadap semua dewi.

61
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:11,620
♪Betapa banyak bunga yang dijumpai
sepanjang jalan layu lalu mekar semula♪

62
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:18,600
♪Barangkali perpisahan yang ditakdirkan
masa kelak tetap akan berulang♪

63
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:21,820
♪Air mata bertukar jadi awan-gemawan♪

64
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:25,180
♪Hujan menitis ke dalam lautan hati♪

65
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:29,120
♪Sampailah awan menghilang,
langit yang cerah mencorakkan♪

66
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:31,580
♪Masa depan♪

67
00:07:34,790 --> 00:07:35,510
Shang Gu.

68
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,270
Setelah awak mewarisi
Perintah Dewa Utama,

69
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:40,950
saya akan meluahkan isi hati saya

70
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,070
kepada awak.

71
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,200
Yue Mi, keluar!

72
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:00,510
Awak mengekori saya sejak tadi.

73
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:02,920
Saya bukannya sengaja.

74
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,070
Saya nak lakukan benda yang
sama dengan awak di Alam Termulia.

75
00:08:06,350 --> 00:08:07,350
Namun, saya balik ke sini

76
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,640
setelah dengar kata-kata Zhi Yang.

77
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:12,000
Jalan menuju ke Alam Dewa adalah sama.

78
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:13,830
Jangan kata saya mengekori awak.

79
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,510
Jalan menuju ke Alam Dewa?

80
00:08:15,510 --> 00:08:16,480
Kita dah sampai Istana Tai Chu!

81
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,550
Apakah yang awak merepek ini?

82
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:19,950
Sudahlah, jangan ikut saya lagi.

83
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,320
Saya bukan sedih sangat.

84
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,830
Pembohong.

85
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,760
Awak tak berani pandang mata orang lain

86
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,040
apabila bercakap bohong.

87
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,350
Awak...

88
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,230
Baiklah.

89
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:30,160
Saya nak Shang Gu mewarisi
takhta dewa utama secepat mungkin.

90
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:32,790
Namun, saya tak sanggup
dia pergi ke Alam Termulia.

91
00:08:33,070 --> 00:08:34,040
Betul.

92
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,720
Sudah tentu saya tak sanggup.

93
00:08:36,230 --> 00:08:37,320
Dia pergi ke Alam Termulia.

94
00:08:37,790 --> 00:08:38,760
Jika dia tercedera lagi...

95
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:39,880
Jika dia ditimpa apa-apa...

96
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:40,400
Awak...

97
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,910
Dia lebih berani daripada kita berdua.

98
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,350
Mungkin dia sudah jadi matang.

99
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,350
Cuma kita yang terlalu risau.

100
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,840
Saya yang tak berguna.

101
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,640
Tian Qi.

102
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:57,840
Mahaguru.

103
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,320
Dewa Agung Tian Qi.

104
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:00,710
Kenapa awak begitu gembira?

105
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,670
Mahaguru.

106
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:04,550
Saya telah menguasai tahap keempat
dalam Enam Teknik Tai Yin.

107
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:08,320
Baru tahap keempat,
awak sudah begitu gembira?

108
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:09,960
Gu Jun telah pun menjadi dewa.

109
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:10,960
Dewa Agung.

110
00:09:11,230 --> 00:09:12,590
Mu Guang tak pernah malas

111
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,640
selepas datang ke Alam Dewa.

112
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,840
Saya berlatih setiap hari.

113
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:20,080
Kenapa awak lepaskan geram
pada anak murid saya?

114
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,760
Satu serangan pun tak dapat tahan.

115
00:09:22,470 --> 00:09:23,320
Tak guna.

116
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,470
Saya tiada apa-apa.

117
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,400
Dewa Agung mengajar saya tadi.

118
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:32,350
Awak bukan bodoh sangat.

119
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,840
Awak pergi dulu.

120
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,350
Ya.

121
00:09:42,350 --> 00:09:43,080
Awak

122
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,840
memang seorang mahaguru yang bingung.

123
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,470
Patutlah kemajuan dia begitu perlahan.

124
00:09:46,590 --> 00:09:47,760
Saya nampak uratnya kurang lancar,

125
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,910
maka saya tolong dia.

126
00:09:49,230 --> 00:09:49,590
Saya...

127
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:50,350
Apa?

128
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:51,710
Masuk dan minum arak.

129
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,440
Tunggulah saya.

130
00:10:00,470 --> 00:10:01,880
(Istana Chao Sheng)
Yang Maha Mulia pergi bertapa

131
00:10:02,350 --> 00:10:03,910
selama seribu tahun.

132
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:06,910
Budak suruhan lain
suka bergosip tentang saya.

133
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,230
Mereka rasa dengki

134
00:10:08,590 --> 00:10:10,350
kerana Yang Maha Mulia suka akan saya.

135
00:10:11,470 --> 00:10:12,710
Apakah yang harus saya buat

136
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,110
jika mereka tak patuh kata-kata saya?

137
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,350
Saya sudah biasa hidup bersendirian

138
00:10:18,350 --> 00:10:19,590
semasa berada di Paya Yuan Ling.

139
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,710
Saya tidak berpengalaman

140
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,910
untuk berinteraksi dengan orang lain.

141
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:27,670
Gu Jun dan Wu Huan,

142
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,200
kuasa rohani saya meningkat lagi.

143
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:30,880
Mari kita bertarung.

144
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,880
Awak datang tepat pada masanya.

145
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,670
Wu Huan, keluarga Mu Guang besar
dan dia pernah memimpin tentera.

146
00:10:35,670 --> 00:10:36,590
Dia mesti ada jalan.

147
00:10:38,110 --> 00:10:38,880
Apakah masalahnya?

148
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,880
(Istana Chao Sheng)
Setelah mahaguru tiada di sini,

149
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:44,200
Wu Huan bimbang

150
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:45,960
dia tak dapat mengendalikan
budak suruhan.

151
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:51,030
Sejak dulu, mereka tidak suka akan saya.

152
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:53,230
Oleh sebab Yang Maha Mulia
menyayangi saya,

153
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,710
mereka tak berani buat apa-apa
di depan saya.

154
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,840
Sekarang...

155
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:00,350
Sebenarnya, awak patut
tunjukkan kuasa awak

156
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:02,790
ketika Yang Maha Mulia tiada di sini.

157
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,790
Tunjukkan kuasa?

158
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:08,320
Saya patut bersyukur
kerana mereka tak buli saya.

159
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:10,710
Walaupun awak ialah
haiwan sakti dewa utama,

160
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,590
awak juga budak suruhan

161
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,960
ketika Yang Maha Mulia berada di sini.

162
00:11:15,710 --> 00:11:17,000
Sekarang, Yang Maha Mulia tiada di sini.

163
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:19,670
Awaklah orang yang paling berkuasa
di Istana Chao Sheng.

164
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:23,030
Awak boleh memilih

165
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:24,280
orang yang berperangai baik.

166
00:11:24,880 --> 00:11:26,000
Awak tidak payah takut kepada

167
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:27,350
mereka yang tidak ikut arahan.

168
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:30,000
Hukum mereka yang lakukan kesalahan.

169
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,230
Kemudian,
awak tunjuk baik kepada mereka.

170
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:33,590
Tak lama kemudian,

171
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:34,880
mereka akan patuh kepada awak.

172
00:11:36,710 --> 00:11:38,000
Taktik ganjaran dan hukum.

173
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,110
(Istana Chao Sheng)

174
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:39,910
Betul.

175
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:43,030
Rahsia untuk memimpin tentera adalah
menjaga perasaan orang lain.

176
00:11:43,710 --> 00:11:44,790
Beri ganjaran dan hukuman
pada masa yang sama.

177
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,470
Cakap memang senang.

178
00:11:47,590 --> 00:11:48,910
Bagaimana kalau
mereka yang tidak ikut arahan

179
00:11:48,910 --> 00:11:50,200
menjadi lebih melampau

180
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,080
dan membuli saya?

181
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,000
Usah risau pasal ini.

182
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,000
Saya berada di sini.

183
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:55,560
Saya akan belasah
sesiapa yang membuli awak.

184
00:11:59,230 --> 00:11:59,960
Baik.

185
00:12:00,470 --> 00:12:01,440
Saya akan cuba.

186
00:12:02,230 --> 00:12:03,110
Saya mesti menjaga Istana Chao Sheng

187
00:12:03,350 --> 00:12:04,590
dengan baik-baik

188
00:12:04,590 --> 00:12:06,000
sepanjang seribu tahun ini.

189
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:07,910
Saya tidak akan memalukan
Yang Maha Mulia.

190
00:12:09,710 --> 00:12:10,710
Awak dapat lakukannya.

191
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:11,960
Oh ya!

192
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:14,470
Awak kata kuasa rohani awak
telah meningkat.

193
00:12:15,150 --> 00:12:17,230
Ini jasa Dewa Agung Tian Qi.

194
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:19,470
Mari berlatih.

195
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:22,200
Baik, kamu berlatih bersama,

196
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,030
agar saling melengkapi.

197
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:25,640
Saya menyediakan teh untuk kamu.

198
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,710
Terima kasih.

199
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:29,550
Terima kasih.

200
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:40,790
Alam Dewa melantik kamu
untuk menjaga Alam Termulia.

201
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,320
Berani kamu melengahkan kerja.

202
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,520
Tahukah kesalahan kamu?

203
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,200
Saya ingat siapa yang datang.

204
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,520
Awak dah diturunkan pangkat.

205
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:47,590
Masih berlagak di sana?

206
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:48,470
Biadab!

207
00:12:48,670 --> 00:12:50,710
Saya ialah dewi atasan yang menguasai
empat musim di Alam Bawah.

208
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:51,550
Berani awak biadab lagi,

209
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,030
saya akan lapor kepada Alam Dewa.

210
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:54,110
Sudahlah.

211
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:56,230
Semua orang tahu
awak dibuang ke alam ini.

212
00:12:56,470 --> 00:12:58,350
Mereka yang dibuang
untuk menjaga Alam Termulia

213
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,110
tak berpeluang
untuk kembali ke Alam Dewa.

214
00:13:00,350 --> 00:13:02,080
Daripada bergaduh dengan saya,

215
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:04,030
lebih baik awak pergi berteduh
di tempat lain.

216
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:06,910
(Shang Gu.)

217
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:10,350
(Suatu hari nanti,
saya akan kembali ke Alam Dewa.)

218
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:12,350
(Awak kena bayar
pengorbanan yang besar.)

219
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,360
♪Dengar♪

220
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,560
♪Monolog semua makhluk♪

221
00:13:39,640 --> 00:13:43,040
♪Di bawah kubah♪

222
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:44,470
♪Lihat♪

223
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,600
♪Pemandangan gunung yang menakjubkan♪

224
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:50,040
♪Datang dan pergi♪

225
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,430
♪Pandang♪

226
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,640
♪Jalan di depan penuh dengan♪

227
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:56,480
♪Kabus tebal♪

228
00:13:56,560 --> 00:13:59,160
♪Berdiri lama♪

229
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,680
♪Di atas awan♪

230
00:14:01,760 --> 00:14:05,830
♪Hidup di luar langit dan bumi♪

231
00:14:05,920 --> 00:14:09,230
♪Masa pinjamkan♪

232
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:11,130
♪Bimasakti kepada saya♪

233
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:14,480
♪Namun, di mana kenalan lama saya?♪

234
00:14:14,560 --> 00:14:16,480
♪Tinggalkan bayang♪

235
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:20,480
♪Yang sering muncul dalam mimpi saya♪

236
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:23,200
♪Selepas mengharungi ribuan ujian♪

237
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:28,140
♪Saya dah berkali-kali menjelma semula♪

238
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:34,010
♪Awak berada di depan mata saya
atau dijarakkan oleh gunung dan lautan?♪

239
